Name: openPrefs                                  
Author: Erwin Santacruz
Date: 02.23.2012
Cookies and cream: http://www.990adjustments.com /                                  
Shout out: hi@990adjustments.com                                    
 
Description: Open the Cinema 4D user preferences folder.
Make it a button for quick access.

Script tested on OS X 10.6.4 and Cinema 4D versions:
CINEMA 4D R12.016
CINEMA 4D R12.032

Install:
Just drop CenterCut in you scripts directory.

